    "description": "<p><strong>LIAN HIN PTE. LTD.</strong></p>\n<p>At Lian Hin, we keep it simple. We weave aesthetics with practical functunality to create products that last and delight, ranging from feature walls to tabletops and vanities.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We have come a long way since our establishment in 1989 as a humble granite dealer and marble dealer. However, unchanging is our commitment to high quality and exceptional service.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Today we have grown into the leading multi-faceted surfaces like Granite, Marble, Quartz and Sintered Surfaces in Singapore.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
